// LOCALHOST
### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get contact by id
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/69b4b9f02a68c26585fad076

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe 2",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "blue",
  "birthday": "1990-01-15"
}

### Update a contact
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/69bb490e849bb06779dc172b
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "green",
  "birthday": "1990-01-15"
}

### Delete a contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/69b4b9f02a68c26585fad076


